Package com.hoddmimes.distributor

Interface DistributorUpdateCallbackIf

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BdxGwyMulticastGroupEntry, DistributorManagementController, GuiSubscriber
    public interface DistributorUpdateCallbackIf
    Subscriber call back interface. When creating a subscriber the application must specify an callback that the distributor will invoke when data the subscriber has an interest in are updated.
